lead_paragraph: Former FIFA presidential candidate Prince Ali Bin Al Hussein of Jordan is concerned about the pace of reform in world soccer's governing body and says new president Gianni Infantino has "no time to lose" in bringing transparency to the organization.

headline.print_headline: Prince Ali Says FIFA Needs to Speed Up Reforms
